node.text:
Behind the scenes I get some unpredictable requests that can be turned into magical orders. While I can’t always manage every request received, I sure do my best to bring whatever strange dreams you have for your significant other’s smoke life to fruition. Even if it’s baked pandas who love jazz band and sunflowers 🤷‍♀️

Interested in off menu customs? Shoot me an email to build a quote and include your idea within 💌 (button in bio)
